{"tid":1578654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突破樽頸】係時候放低陰謀論","createTime":"2019-09-18T08:20:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T09:50:52.000Z","uid":60539,"like":29,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"85b78820a564ccd44d8b605fa7c125db3ab3f470","tid":1578654,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:20:02.000Z","msg":"希望大家暫時將陰謀論放低<br />\n因為死人係鐵一般既事實<br />\n再陰謀論都人死不能復生<br />\n只有擊敗政府先可以還死者清白<br />\n<br />\n依加我地太依賴勇武衝擊<br />\n我地已經好多手足被捕<br />\n一定要開新戰線幫前線分擔壓力<br />\n<br />\n我地宗旨係be water<br />\n要變幻莫測 無固定形態<br />\n想捉都捉唔緊<br />\n所以我地需要不停變調<br />\n否質只會係玩緊泥漿摔角<br />\n烏克蘭之所以成功<br />\n就係佢地變調<br />\n由死守轉為號召攻入總統府<br />\n最終總統敗走<br />\n<br />\n其實每次新抗爭方法<br />\n對方都一定手忙腳亂<br />\nifc唱紅歌就係個好例子<br />\n完全比我地lead住<br />\n只能跟住我地既腳步走<br />\n<br />\n我地要靠小站份人實行新既抗爭手法<br />\n再號召然後遍地開花<br />\n所以要鼓勵所有人一齊發揮創意<br />\n無論咩嘗試都好<br />\n一定要有人行出第一步<br />\n可能你果步就係通往成功既一步<br />\n<br />\n唔好再期望政府帶領我地走出困局<br />\n我地要自己行出呢個死局"},{"pid":"7f2b684df07dac757bf19982941c52bfe7bd994c","tid":1578654,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:20:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「929全球集會抗赤納粹」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界一齊對準極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577380</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWqVmOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWqVmOV.jpg&h=075c7745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1tov9s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1tov9s.png&h=0af09f95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"933a3876864211afa77fc90b99c2efa057d4231f","tid":1578654,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:21:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"